Subject: [PATCH 5.15.y 5/7] x86/bugs: Use ALTERNATIVE() instead of
 mds_user_clear static key
Message-ID: <20240304-delay-verw-backport-5-15-y-v1-5-fd02afc00fec@linux.intel.com>
X-Mailer: b4 0.12.3
References: <20240304-delay-verw-backport-5-15-y-v1-0-fd02afc00fec@linux.intel.com>
Precedence: bulk
X-Mailing-List: stable@vger.kernel.org
